    <p>Roma FC</p>
    <p>commonly referred to as simply Roma  is a professional Italian football club based in Rome. Founded by a merger in 1927, Roma have participated in the top-tier of Italian football for all of their existence except for 1951–52. For their 64th season in a row  Roma are competing in Serie A for the 2015–16 season.</p>
    
